          "$t": "2014-10-07T10:26:31.662+02:00"
        },
        "title": {
          "type": "text",
          "$t": "Náučný chodník Divinka - Veľký vrch"
        },
        "content": {
          "type": "html",
          "$t": "<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\nNaše Občianske združenie Hradiská, spolu s obcou Divinka, Archeologickým ústavom SAV, Považským múzeom Žilina,&nbsp;Komposesorátom Veľký vrch, Hradisko Divinka&nbsp;a s finančnou pomocou nadácie Pontis &nbsp;a Nadačného fondu Kia Motors &nbsp;Slovakia, vytvorilo&nbsp;na hradisku Veľký vrch v Divinke nový náučný chodník o dejinách hradiska a najvýznamnejších archeologických kultúrach, ktoré obývali hradisko.&nbsp;</div>\n<br />\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEg95DVSIhteAX3YNOeFdr6_6uoH3xL2sXc4iBKerXvfmJE33ymYctThw145WIwQZNmi4L-U1wAk6sqU5UpaHkUnudVB1FRWZrI2i-HW92hFft8owIqF_astOfLPI_OhKIOnSYVZPrT0Pgs/s1600/Mapka+naucnychodnik.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEg95DVSIhteAX3YNOeFdr6_6uoH3xL2sXc4iBKerXvfmJE33ymYctThw145WIwQZNmi4L-U1wAk6sqU5UpaHkUnudVB1FRWZrI2i-HW92hFft8owIqF_astOfLPI_OhKIOnSYVZPrT0Pgs/s1600/Mapka+naucnychodnik.jpg\" height=\"212\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\nNáučný chodník Vás z centra obce dovedie až na vrcholovú časť hradiska a počas Vášho putovania sa dozviete z našich siedmych informačných tabúľ množstvo &nbsp;zaujímavých vecí z našej dávnej histórie. Počas tvorby tabúľ sa nám vďaka veľkej ústretovosti Archeologického ústavu (PhDr. Gabriel Fusek, Csc.), ktorý po odbornej aj jazykovej stránke prísnym okom skorigoval všetky použité texty a Považského múzea v Žiline (Mgr. Andrea Slaná), ktorá nám poskytla unikátne fotografie nálezov zo starších výskumov z hradiska, ako aj vďaka ďalším spolupracovníkom, podarilo dosiahnuť odborne aj vizuálne kvalitný náučný chodník, obsahujúci viaceré doposiaľ nepublikované obrázky a informácie, ktorý veríme že zaujme všetkých milovníkov histórie.</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<br /></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"tr-caption-container\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;\"><tbody>\n<tr><td style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhTF4CX0M2wjsos6e0JKmcuy50RJ9AjAwNA5rj8BqYZNKSAM1BPL0oTCVsexg5bIzNhzovk8fPlM8OVOvSU7SH8K53udUPTq9NwacqoSIELkn4lOLwcm_u6tOd_9uguuwO4O66g1PyU8Oo/s1600/Divinka_tabula1_lowres.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhTF4CX0M2wjsos6e0JKmcuy50RJ9AjAwNA5rj8BqYZNKSAM1BPL0oTCVsexg5bIzNhzovk8fPlM8OVOvSU7SH8K53udUPTq9NwacqoSIELkn4lOLwcm_u6tOd_9uguuwO4O66g1PyU8Oo/s1600/Divinka_tabula1_lowres.jpg\" height=\"226\" width=\"320\" /></a></td></tr>\n<tr><td class=\"tr-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\">úvodná tabuľa nášho nového náučného chodníka</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<span id=\"goog_235218349\"></span><span id=\"goog_235218350\"></span><br /></div>\n<div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\nOtvorenie náučného chodníka sa konalo 31.8. 2014 v rámci akcie Staroslovanská Divinka. Zástupca nášho združenia Čendo tu slávnostne pokrstil celý náučný chodník a potom sa všetci účastníci vydali po stopách našich predkov aby sa oboznámili so všetkými siedmymi tabuľami náučného chodníka. Kvalitný odborný výklad im pritom poskytla archeologička Mgr. Andrea Slaná.</div>\n<br />\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"tr-caption-container\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;\"><tbody>\n<tr><td style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEil4O3xF-o7Bsq-S13Rj0n7OjSnopMcTWv-hW5ofIFYUcjNgMhOku5aVk3VZt2Wb6w1atpPCsgIqSvMg8-scul2gOXKUNmSqjs7WhLyoSy2eQIoNjiLfSSaV8-Ysc4jstsMIB9xIjSftGI/s1600/10410484_10202470794667258_2378311738645570988_n.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEil4O3xF-o7Bsq-S13Rj0n7OjSnopMcTWv-hW5ofIFYUcjNgMhOku5aVk3VZt2Wb6w1atpPCsgIqSvMg8-scul2gOXKUNmSqjs7WhLyoSy2eQIoNjiLfSSaV8-Ysc4jstsMIB9xIjSftGI/s1600/10410484_10202470794667258_2378311738645570988_n.jpg\" height=\"240\" width=\"320\" /></a></td></tr>\n<tr><td class=\"tr-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"background-color: white; color: #141823; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, 'lucida grande', tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; text-align: left;\">Prvá infotabuľa sa nachádza v centre obce pri autobusovej zastávke a turistov navedie na náučný chodník.&nbsp;</span></td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<br />\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"tr-caption-container\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;\"><tbody>\n<tr><td style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjY87WADjmTmpT2LMLQgGwekYHC8TGwlFVGvCXUIJQzYmnqBsSEPv8biCm5CCzhWy19ad5EcfD4Ws0Hr3NCHHJ2_vdd6Bi7osS4HjZmNTv00DxtGtpu3Jpx_5otw6Wc_rkp7eZNsSX1HCo/s1600/10419579_10202470797547330_7339559485700718412_n.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjY87WADjmTmpT2LMLQgGwekYHC8TGwlFVGvCXUIJQzYmnqBsSEPv8biCm5CCzhWy19ad5EcfD4Ws0Hr3NCHHJ2_vdd6Bi7osS4HjZmNTv00DxtGtpu3Jpx_5otw6Wc_rkp7eZNsSX1HCo/s1600/10419579_10202470797547330_7339559485700718412_n.jpg\" height=\"240\" width=\"320\" /></a></td></tr>\n<tr><td class=\"tr-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"background-color: white; color: #141823; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, 'lucida grande', tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; text-align: left;\">Čendo ju požehnal za všetkých 7 tabúľ, hneď na začiatku náučného chodníka&nbsp;</span><br />\n<span style=\"background-color: white; color: #141823; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, 'lucida grande', tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; text-align: left;\">za prítomnosti reportéra RTVS a mnohých záujemcov o históriu</span></td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<br />\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi40PX0b9SLW5wBXCHORfUFsQXDLGRWJCKIarrYhYA9sLrvtAfqTOLCO2LGov_boYFiDeupFdj4AsQux07Rx8ljiP3Yb9055cAg_LHwdRDDZT_PubFRgUoUChkAv4_rlXZR_nOslE3OGqM/s1600/c%CC%8Cendo.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi40PX0b9SLW5wBXCHORfUFsQXDLGRWJCKIarrYhYA9sLrvtAfqTOLCO2LGov_boYFiDeupFdj4AsQux07Rx8ljiP3Yb9055cAg_LHwdRDDZT_PubFRgUoUChkAv4_rlXZR_nOslE3OGqM/s1600/c%CC%8Cendo.jpg\" height=\"320\" width=\"216\" /></a></div>\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n</div>\n<br />\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"tr-caption-container\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;\"><tbody>\n<tr><td style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEieH3agpmh7KmJuG85JEgvzXBxd88lEPPOoj954B_G90gpRIJa1fdKZIWqwCiD9ySZHF6kTR5Gp56k3kvtO1wxiRQG0-p7qTaaYIjmcH9ir7lcqdafxQ6CWciGDUdzp3GXByZQjppv_M0w/s1600/10646843_10202471175356775_1426566541495284262_n.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEieH3agpmh7KmJuG85JEgvzXBxd88lEPPOoj954B_G90gpRIJa1fdKZIWqwCiD9ySZHF6kTR5Gp56k3kvtO1wxiRQG0-p7qTaaYIjmcH9ir7lcqdafxQ6CWciGDUdzp3GXByZQjppv_M0w/s1600/10646843_10202471175356775_1426566541495284262_n.jpg\" height=\"240\" width=\"320\" /></a></td></tr>\n<tr><td class=\"tr-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Druhá tabuľa sa nachádza na mieste, kde za začína chodník vedúci na Veľký vrch</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<br />\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"tr-caption-container\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;\"><tbody>\n<tr><td style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjP0c1vv70AejLcpI6rz9dhr-aeL8Y5P6bjXwI51clYOwNC13RKqKXYjDhYbq0wKSTiI4JffyKDKI4NuFmIn3xihyphenhyphensDzUucsQ5tAgzaVoWDGMQKSBM-DDNUY_CVQmh5sJvakKPufqkxMK8/s1600/10659307_10202470801267423_2291482025244817330_n.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjP0c1vv70AejLcpI6rz9dhr-aeL8Y5P6bjXwI51clYOwNC13RKqKXYjDhYbq0wKSTiI4JffyKDKI4NuFmIn3xihyphenhyphensDzUucsQ5tAgzaVoWDGMQKSBM-DDNUY_CVQmh5sJvakKPufqkxMK8/s1600/10659307_10202470801267423_2291482025244817330_n.jpg\" height=\"240\" width=\"320\" /></a></td></tr>\n<tr><td class=\"tr-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Archeologička Mgr. Andrea Slaná pri tretej tabuli (Lužická kultúra)</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<br />\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEht1lFacc7NuGXHM90YZ4l7v3IqmvLApL40JqfcXxbV84cnLr9JXm5ZMkJvM1DHLnHJC3LKnFvfcawWsqwHzb6lt_Iwz3LncOmtjuEw-TFd3j0ci-SKh0WkAJtF78YmPoSRlxIcq4gUuZk/s1600/10641155_10202470804827512_3987382795788846580_n.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEht1lFacc7NuGXHM90YZ4l7v3IqmvLApL40JqfcXxbV84cnLr9JXm5ZMkJvM1DHLnHJC3LKnFvfcawWsqwHzb6lt_Iwz3LncOmtjuEw-TFd3j0ci-SKh0WkAJtF78YmPoSRlxIcq4gUuZk/s1600/10641155_10202470804827512_3987382795788846580_n.jpg\" height=\"240\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<br />\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"tr-caption-container\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;\"><tbody>\n<tr><td style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhnuWOTXk4XbBAzyXCQ8MA3DPOWKSmnr534xmp1rSm9h5xOZvhgNf4Tq9JR0Ug1uLSRjumGc8DHVGTJp-afGxtYgZ9vyxJSdXwdY9CBBhyIViSzoP5_eL6nKQAHJMlLQYzJrWItHwmrxv0/s1600/10645125_10202470803307474_1624112215670323646_n.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhnuWOTXk4XbBAzyXCQ8MA3DPOWKSmnr534xmp1rSm9h5xOZvhgNf4Tq9JR0Ug1uLSRjumGc8DHVGTJp-afGxtYgZ9vyxJSdXwdY9CBBhyIViSzoP5_eL6nKQAHJMlLQYzJrWItHwmrxv0/s1600/10645125_10202470803307474_1624112215670323646_n.jpg\" height=\"240\" width=\"320\" /></a></td></tr>\n<tr><td class=\"tr-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Štvrtá tabuľa sa nachádza pri turistickom prístrešku a je venovaná púchovskej kultúre všeobecne</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<br />\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"tr-caption-container\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;\"><tbody>\n<tr><td style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi4CG1zB1RjM0DrX-8ZDwfCFkUzeHb9Wohvzt5FIip9bjN0xFkys78ZZqYeMiFMH0Q9JHyBL4o7JbQu0YnaxiusT6ctuHDHNhUYbeAj78ML9ij4jW_mUjVwrBiE2J1JiPFhXynaCICO9oI/s1600/1902808_10202470800707409_3510548886269444039_n.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi4CG1zB1RjM0DrX-8ZDwfCFkUzeHb9Wohvzt5FIip9bjN0xFkys78ZZqYeMiFMH0Q9JHyBL4o7JbQu0YnaxiusT6ctuHDHNhUYbeAj78ML9ij4jW_mUjVwrBiE2J1JiPFhXynaCICO9oI/s1600/1902808_10202470800707409_3510548886269444039_n.jpg\" height=\"240\" width=\"320\" /></a></td></tr>\n<tr><td class=\"tr-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Napriek nie ideálnemu počasiu bola pekná účasť</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<br />\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"tr-caption-container\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;\"><tbody>\n<tr><td style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhYezT1n38yOrGCaVIK6AvQY-WsBa8j2v8wIqFgmJaA4BHkvcdKSZnbm9ujwJL0Z4-b6NsNGjFRcjJo9avx1kapZfIE-rDfjt3KxIzN_wcnNi6VSw4q16Q6JJb74RmbOQiEzFxS5IRV4O0/s1600/10646715_10202470806307549_4008509993604950270_n.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhYezT1n38yOrGCaVIK6AvQY-WsBa8j2v8wIqFgmJaA4BHkvcdKSZnbm9ujwJL0Z4-b6NsNGjFRcjJo9avx1kapZfIE-rDfjt3KxIzN_wcnNi6VSw4q16Q6JJb74RmbOQiEzFxS5IRV4O0/s1600/10646715_10202470806307549_4008509993604950270_n.jpg\" height=\"240\" width=\"320\" /></a></td></tr>\n<tr><td class=\"tr-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\">piata tabuľa (Veľká Morava) &nbsp;sa nachádza na mieste, kde poľná cesta pretína vonkajší val opevnenia</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<br />\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"tr-caption-container\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;\"><tbody>\n<tr><td style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh4kHLrazj0rN0GyzN4IYsg6gKvFaeIBfQxw4MIVVzC4TnC7VrLKY03A6pymmAMDmPUuwrKOgr3I-SrLQQDUa4mnj5Rg1nI_A5bADprceiO-h9lXcjazns1-eyK_zUrDpnmtRaPBWHxHVY/s1600/6.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh4kHLrazj0rN0GyzN4IYsg6gKvFaeIBfQxw4MIVVzC4TnC7VrLKY03A6pymmAMDmPUuwrKOgr3I-SrLQQDUa4mnj5Rg1nI_A5bADprceiO-h9lXcjazns1-eyK_zUrDpnmtRaPBWHxHVY/s1600/6.jpg\" height=\"240\" width=\"320\" /></a></td></tr>\n<tr><td class=\"tr-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Na mieste, kde pôvodne stála vstupná brána na vrcholovú časť hradiska sme umiestnili šiestu tabuľu, venovanú konkrétnym nálezom z Veľkého vrchu z praveku a staroveku</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<br />\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjGUfwYjPynn8nL3E_xGDvfP5F9h8cCDkD0QiekpK2OYdVOxAa_HU2g_mNatzzcyqx92nEAD2A55UwI32Lx7tJW2tLVp5vdttepsRyGnr_qQWUipYgo6LtkB7kiBHrrUL0PJha24E93s2g/s1600/10429268_10202470807707584_6601096487858320033_n.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjGUfwYjPynn8nL3E_xGDvfP5F9h8cCDkD0QiekpK2OYdVOxAa_HU2g_mNatzzcyqx92nEAD2A55UwI32Lx7tJW2tLVp5vdttepsRyGnr_qQWUipYgo6LtkB7kiBHrrUL0PJha24E93s2g/s1600/10429268_10202470807707584_6601096487858320033_n.jpg\" height=\"240\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<br />\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"tr-caption-container\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;\"><tbody>\n<tr><td style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEg3qHlLPZJiCJFsFXBW6NHe4Yx7FXbJZDUWV09QJYQEb78xKDYkF6fz10ykgjaaF501duMijcBJcKfubnfW513C0lJJwE-Ino8ty58JhYvBnWnnXJEeYbZLK3okU8wmxnG7YUTEYWX6hyphenhyphenM/s1600/10593128_10202470809707634_289806678401387306_n.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEg3qHlLPZJiCJFsFXBW6NHe4Yx7FXbJZDUWV09QJYQEb78xKDYkF6fz10ykgjaaF501duMijcBJcKfubnfW513C0lJJwE-Ino8ty58JhYvBnWnnXJEeYbZLK3okU8wmxnG7YUTEYWX6hyphenhyphenM/s1600/10593128_10202470809707634_289806678401387306_n.jpg\" height=\"240\" width=\"320\" /></a></td></tr>\n<tr><td class=\"tr-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Siedma tabuľa je umiestnená na vyhliadke a je venovaná nálezom z Veľkého vrchu zo slovanského obdobia</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<br />\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEipDodWks21VKhAhiZeCBwTUC4kczuCO4DvoQvOaJ_tZwsvEpMY9PaPAK7hQoKQ_sX_KroI3eYysEpeWDC5p3PdNvk1TY29QCUEcsEslTHU7Xv9ZirLjVtCSgHk65l8Q7S83uGDzMpmpA0/s1600/prva%CC%81.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEipDodWks21VKhAhiZeCBwTUC4kczuCO4DvoQvOaJ_tZwsvEpMY9PaPAK7hQoKQ_sX_KroI3eYysEpeWDC5p3PdNvk1TY29QCUEcsEslTHU7Xv9ZirLjVtCSgHk65l8Q7S83uGDzMpmpA0/s1600/prva%CC%81.jpg\" height=\"223\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<br />\n<br />\nPo ukončení archeologického výskumu na hradisku doplníme na Veľký vrch ďalšie 2 tabule, a tie budú zahŕňať výsledky najnovších výskumov, ktoré na hradisku práve prebiehajú. <br />\n<br />\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n</div>\n<br />\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"tr-caption-container\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;\"><tbody>\n<tr><td style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi8rbl4K0V_bVVctod2UsvYNMuF1FvK7CQo7e5D0tRlp6bOivpvhl1UY6T2TayVzC1axRIvgq1w-kgyk_fbkuDJyX6Q-xOLonduH8qMj1HYTXHkpPl7JJ3UxccmV6e83atK7T7htDPJzP4/s1600/10583062_611197622327394_638314878377092813_o.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi8rbl4K0V_bVVctod2UsvYNMuF1FvK7CQo7e5D0tRlp6bOivpvhl1UY6T2TayVzC1axRIvgq1w-kgyk_fbkuDJyX6Q-xOLonduH8qMj1HYTXHkpPl7JJ3UxccmV6e83atK7T7htDPJzP4/s1600/10583062_611197622327394_638314878377092813_o.jpg\" height=\"226\" width=\"320\" /></a></td></tr>\n<tr><td class=\"tr-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Tabuľa č. 2</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"tr-caption-container\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;\"><tbody>\n<tr><td style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEghNr5U21ZVpHEYCgxvAhBwppt8nJwUq0bMlsaqj6q5oVJu2epRSar22uW5tAQRUXZAGt48jDNBkkHivgE19xwQBFoMy7Fd1tfGPBltKkPj45S7rW98QDlHI_m-xfeaWeWXSXBLaOIDeg0/s1600/10499358_611197675660722_3029285982714367344_o.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEghNr5U21ZVpHEYCgxvAhBwppt8nJwUq0bMlsaqj6q5oVJu2epRSar22uW5tAQRUXZAGt48jDNBkkHivgE19xwQBFoMy7Fd1tfGPBltKkPj45S7rW98QDlHI_m-xfeaWeWXSXBLaOIDeg0/s1600/10499358_611197675660722_3029285982714367344_o.jpg\" height=\"226\" width=\"320\" /></a></td></tr>\n<tr><td class=\"tr-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Tabuľa č. 3</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"tr-caption-container\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;\"><tbody>\n<tr><td style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjNlSwMsVV2XMYl3xq3OlQ2u6THYS9DVFYF135sYVKo5331lV021E0vkE3gBi3htic-y_IjUh2BuvouVHIAK8rxMCfyZxfusnU6GEaRcMV78oEQIVshQYHwOks-vaddrZ2e_i7loYkDGeg/s1600/10494940_611197722327384_33976834454616_o.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjNlSwMsVV2XMYl3xq3OlQ2u6THYS9DVFYF135sYVKo5331lV021E0vkE3gBi3htic-y_IjUh2BuvouVHIAK8rxMCfyZxfusnU6GEaRcMV78oEQIVshQYHwOks-vaddrZ2e_i7loYkDGeg/s1600/10494940_611197722327384_33976834454616_o.jpg\" height=\"226\" width=\"320\" /></a></td></tr>\n<tr><td class=\"tr-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Tabuľa č. 4</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"tr-caption-container\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;\"><tbody>\n<tr><td style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEg9DqZKqkZhX-SLig_xT7EkPR7YxB9fnqfhaNuKIZgB6TTf3bgr27B54FddWR9_gMWFwMSa461krccBNcDrQNPwbSbTJWR_v0JrehdnQMEnKiw0K154Q8i7iKXA4BITbqg3ToNv_l7DHxU/s1600/10580939_611197792327377_8472018993576283417_o.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEg9DqZKqkZhX-SLig_xT7EkPR7YxB9fnqfhaNuKIZgB6TTf3bgr27B54FddWR9_gMWFwMSa461krccBNcDrQNPwbSbTJWR_v0JrehdnQMEnKiw0K154Q8i7iKXA4BITbqg3ToNv_l7DHxU/s1600/10580939_611197792327377_8472018993576283417_o.jpg\" height=\"226\" width=\"320\" /></a></td></tr>\n<tr><td class=\"tr-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Tabuľa č. 5</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"tr-caption-container\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;\"><tbody>\n<tr><td style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi8xoiel0lPnLAJ1wuiQCJAaAonm_zvXHA4O-nhvPzcluI0EhmkvLpyuyxZDZ6QArj3Iwv8owu0VJTmY4YJlNPe3asQ4gyp-054nGCVa5jGVgvx6ahZfUSpblSyt0QL-pzaAoZTaEf2b_I/s1600/10454215_611197852327371_7369167426320042397_o.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi8xoiel0lPnLAJ1wuiQCJAaAonm_zvXHA4O-nhvPzcluI0EhmkvLpyuyxZDZ6QArj3Iwv8owu0VJTmY4YJlNPe3asQ4gyp-054nGCVa5jGVgvx6ahZfUSpblSyt0QL-pzaAoZTaEf2b_I/s1600/10454215_611197852327371_7369167426320042397_o.jpg\" height=\"226\" width=\"320\" /></a></td></tr>\n<tr><td class=\"tr-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Tabuľa č. 6</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"tr-caption-container\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;\"><tbody>\n<tr><td style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhROtCo8pNGTe7UX6TUSjob1CY1iSJwrhjwOzbrZut5MYdL5JTMaEYhEJ81cUBDNUpDsvtwfCULWs8gC480v-QClW9lxXckbI-bNujFWIBKeEzCumJ2a1jc8Sc-KACXUyccr3KbalbrxrI/s1600/10562517_611197908994032_7210496297910123879_o.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhROtCo8pNGTe7UX6TUSjob1CY1iSJwrhjwOzbrZut5MYdL5JTMaEYhEJ81cUBDNUpDsvtwfCULWs8gC480v-QClW9lxXckbI-bNujFWIBKeEzCumJ2a1jc8Sc-KACXUyccr3KbalbrxrI/s1600/10562517_611197908994032_7210496297910123879_o.jpg\" height=\"226\" width=\"320\" /></a></td></tr>\n<tr><td class=\"tr-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Tabuľa č. 7</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\nNa záver &nbsp;ešte treba poďakovať pracovníkom Krajského pamiatkového úradu v Žiline, ktorí správne konanie o povolení umiestnenia tabúľ (ktoré v tomto prípade muselo prebehnúť, kedže hradisko je NKP) zrealizovali prioritne v skrátených lehotách.</div>\n<br />\nPrijdite sa všetci pozrieť na náš náučný chodník, ktorý veríme, že bude mať dlhú životnosť, rovnako ako naše ostatné tabule...<br />\n<br /></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\nOrgoň</div>\n"
